name: Cyberse Gadget
description: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 Level 2 or lower monster in your GY; Special Summon it Defense Position, but it has its effects negated. If this card is sent from the field to the GY: You can Special Summon 1 "Gadget Token" (Cyberse/LIGHT/Level 2/ATK 0/DEF 0). You can only use this effect of "Cyberse Gadget" once per turn.
